org.encryptor4j.test

Class MessageTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.encryptor4j.test.MessageTest

  • public class MessageTest
extends java.lang.Object

    Unit test that tests message encryption using the Encryptor class.

    Tests the following algorithms using multiple block modes when possible:

    • AES
    • DES
    • RSA
    • Blowfish
    • ARC4
    • RC2
    • RC4
    • RC5
    Author:
    Martin
    See Also:
    http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/guides/security/StandardNames.html#Cipher
